description:
This is a 6 minute workout called 'Hamstring Stretch' from the channel Peter Donohoe.
The workout falls under Flexibility/Stretching.
It's suitable for Beginner and Intermediate fitness levels.
You'll need Other for this workout.
The workout has a The Reboot Workout and The Comfort Moves vibe.
The The Reboot Workout vibe means Deep stretch, low stress, total-body refresh. This is especially good for Recovery days, stress relief, post-travel stiffness. The The Comfort Moves vibe means Safe, cozy, feel-good movement. This is especially good for Those who want to move but need it to feel easy and accessible..
The technique difficulty is Beginner and Intermediate.
The effort required is Light.

Original workout description: Gain flexibility in your hamstrings as Pete leads you through simple, hamstring stretches using a band. Resistance band, strap, or towel required. ...
